1
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,760
Breaking news.

2
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:24,920
Lu Group, deeply mired
in a financial crisis,

3
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
has suffered another heavy blow.

4
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:28,039
The group that provided the overseas funds
it relied on for turnover

5
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,510
suddenly announced today that,

6
00:01:29,510 --> 00:01:31,280
as Lu Group failed to meet

7
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,710
the key terms of
multiple financing agreements,

8
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,789
all subsequent fund disbursements
are frozen effective immediately,

9
00:01:36,789 --> 00:01:40,390
and collateral disposal procedures
are officially initiated.

10
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,430
Key terms?

11
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:47,509
Those are impossible tasks.

12
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:50,430
It's a trap.

13
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,310
It was a trap from the beginning!

14
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,920
They never intended to help us.

15
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,370
They just wanted to ruin us.

16
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,640
Mr. Lu.

17
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,760
We're domed.

18
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:10,610
All the money was used
to pay the previous debt

19
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:11,960
and the high interest

20
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,910
on their first tranche of funds.

21
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:16,930
Now the follow-up funding is cut off.

22
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:18,680
The debt has fully erupted.

23
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,520
Suppliers sued us.

24
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,320
Banks have frozen our accounts.

25
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:26,770
Global Capital has activated
its mortgage rights.

26
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,060
We can't keep our core subsidiaries.

27
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:34,960
Mr. Lu.

28
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:38,320
The people from the court
are already on their way.

29
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,710
Very good, Su Xia.

30
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,910
You didn't let me down.

31
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,280
Right now, Lu Fan is experiencing

32
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,480
the most impressive moment of his life.

33
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,120
When he comes back,

34
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,310
he'll find this place is hell.

35
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,310
Let's go.

36
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,430
I want to see him.

37
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,920
Five minutes.

38
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,100
Three minutes will do.

39
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,340
I just want to say a word to him.

40
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,910
Su Xia, are you kidding me?

41
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,840
You told me you're going to see him?

42
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,030
Why are you seeing him?

43
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,360
What are you going to say to him?

44
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,560
"Sorry, I lied to you.

45
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,280
This is just a setup.

46
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,680
I'm here to destroy you."

47
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,540
Or "I can't bear to part with you"?

48
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,000
Su Xia, look at me.

49
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,680
Do you really have feelings for him?

50
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,240
Have you forgotten our past?

51
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,560
I haven't.

52
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,950
I just want to say goodbye to him.

53
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,840
Lu Fan will soon lose everything,

54
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,240
and his reputation will be ruined.

55
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,430
Haven't we endured for over ten years

56
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:11,240
just for this moment?

57
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,150
Now you tell me you want to see him?

58
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,800
You still pity him.

59
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,220
You must leave here with me right now.

60
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:24,510
Whether you want to play along or not,

61
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,190
it's not up to you.

62
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:26,120
I won't go.

63
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:27,390
Let me go.

64
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:30,480
Xiao Qi, let me go.

65
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,240
Xiao Qi.

66
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,360
I haven't seen you for a few days.

67
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:02,090
You look so miserable now.

68
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,310
By the way,

69
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,080
your hideout got busted.

70
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,640
You must be upset, right?

71
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:14,640
What are you doing here?

72
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,160
I've already

73
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,070
paid you back

74
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,670
the principal and interest.

75
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,430
We are even.

76
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,480
Even?

77
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:26,000
Mr. Lu,

78
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,190
are you kidding,

79
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,680
or calling me an idiot?

80
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,720
Let me tell you,

81
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,020
I haven't received a single dime.

82
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,930
That's impossible.

83
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,480
How is this possible?

84
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:45,240
I told He Fei to handle it.

85
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:46,720
He even told me

86
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,680
he handed the money to you himself,

87
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,210
and you received the money.

88
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:52,800
Yes.

89
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,600
There's a receipt.

90
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,270
Lu Fan.

91
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,630
Cut the crap!

92
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,240
My men are all here.

93
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,000
Ask him.

94
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,600
Did he receive a single dime?

95
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:05,510
Receipt?

96
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,750
Bullshit!

97
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:11,160
Who is He Fei?

98
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,170
Hey, are you trying to dodge your debt?

99
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,040
Let me make a call.

100
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,360
Let me make a call.

101
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:33,360
Sorry. The number you have dialed
is powered off.

102
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,630
Come with me.

103
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:49,190
Usual rules.

104
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:50,390
Beat me,

105
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:52,400
and I'll let you see him.

106
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,600
Mr. Lu, I took the money.

107
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:13,510
Don't bother looking for me.

108
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,920
Just consider it my reward

109
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,120
for all these years.

110
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:40,680
Hurry up!

111
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,680
Don't let him get away.

112
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,070
Stop!

113
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:42,950
Stop!

114
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,190
Isn't this Mr. Lu?

115
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:18,000
Han Qi.

116
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,930
Where are you going in such a hurry?

117
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:25,680
Mr. Lu,

118
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:29,360
come with me.

119
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,200
As for the money you owe,

120
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:34,190
you should give an explanation.

121
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,390
Mr. Lu.

122
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,870
Look at me.

123
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,120
Look at me.

124
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,840
Who beat you up like this?

125
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:35,090
You're beaten so badly
that I can barely recognize you.

126
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:36,510
Why is it you?

127
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,910
Is Long your man too?

128
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,120
Mr. Lu.

129
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,440
That's all because of you.

130
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:51,480
You forced me into a corner back then.

131
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,480
I had no choice but to choose
this line of work.

132
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,080
I had no choice.
I needed to make a living.

133
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,390
I will pay you back the money.

134
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,760
Release me immediately.

135
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,150
Lu Fan.

136
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,720
I think you've been on your high horse
for too long.

137
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,640
Are you ordering me?

138
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,120
Are you bluffing?

139
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,540
How can you pay me
back in your current state?

140
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,910
Besides, I don't want your money.

141
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:29,910
What I want is for you
to wish you were dead,

142
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,840
like a stray dog,

143
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,840
kneeling in front of me and begging.

144
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:41,360
Do you know what my life motto is?

145
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:43,960
Be ruthless.

146
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:44,880
Dare to sell.

147
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,240
Be shameless.

148
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,270
We have plenty of time.

149
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,090
We can take our time.

150
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,240
Louder.

151
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,630
Hello.

152
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,080
Su Xia, do you know where Fan is?

153
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,650
I haven't seen him for days.

154
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,100
Where is Lu Fan?

155
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,440
He's gone. Did you do it?

156
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,030
Su Xia.

157
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,080
You know me better than
anyone in the world.

158
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,630
If I resorted to such methods,

159
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,360
Lu Fan wouldn't be alive today.

160
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,870
I can't find him now.

161
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,030
Can you help me?

162
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,150
I beg you.

163
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,840
Are you crazy, Su Xia?

164
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,200
You want me to find him for you?

165
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:05,390
Why should I?

166
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,550
I'll go by myself.

167
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:16,390
Fine.

168
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,650
I won't help you find him

169
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,750
unless you are willing to marry me,

170
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:24,270
being my lawful wife.

171
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:28,230
Then, I will leave no stone unturned
to find Lu Fan for you.

172
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:31,200
Why are you still thinking about using me?

173
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,460
Using me to drive him to his death?

174
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:38,150
You think I'm using you?

175
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,720
Do you still think I'm using you?

176
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,080
Don't you?

177
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,600
The Lu family has long been destroyed.

178
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,870
Lu Fan has already lost everything.
Isn't that enough?

179
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:48,960
It's not enough.

180
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:53,750
I told you.

181
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,630
The Lu family

182
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,440
must be ruined,

183
00:12:58,510 --> 00:13:00,040
and its people must perish.

184
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,030
Xia.

185
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:16,150
Su Xia, I found Lu Fan.

186
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,480
Send me the address now.

187
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:21,130
Xiao Qi, stop right there!

188
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,870
Su Xia is an individual.

189
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:28,440
She has her own choices and future.

190
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,480
She is not your pawn,

191
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:32,550
or a tool for your revenge.

192
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:35,120
She has grown up now.

193
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,510
She is no longer the child
who can only rely on you

194
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:39,630
and be instilled with hatred by you.

195
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:43,120
Please don't be so cruel to her.

196
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,790
Cruel?

197
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,120
What gives you the right to call me cruel?

198
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:57,000
Who brought her here?

199
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:02,120
Who pandered to that bastard Lu Zhen'an?

200
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,240
Let me tell you.

201
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,720
When Su Xia was locked in the dark room,

202
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:09,630
being humiliated and abused,

203
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:10,890
crying and screaming,

204
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:14,410
and calling for her sister for help,
where were you?

205
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,870
Where were you?

206
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,480
No.

207
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,270
Xiao Qi.

208
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:23,730
It was you, Su Dong,

209
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,320
who brought your younger sister

210
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:29,630
into this scary hell!

211
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,440
I had no choice back then!

212
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,200
I had no choice!

213
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:32,910
Nonsense!

214
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,680
You were just scared.

215
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:38,030
You were just a coward.

216
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:39,870
You just couldn't bear to let go of

217
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,440
what the Lu family gave you.

218
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:43,030
You couldn't bear to lose

219
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:46,790
your hypocritical status as a lady.

220
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,360
It was me, Xiao Qi,

221
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,360
who pulled her out of the mud.

222
00:14:52,870 --> 00:14:53,910
I told her

223
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,440
that begging for mercy is useless.

224
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,600
Crying is useless.

225
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,370
Only by getting stronger,

226
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,390
only by hating,

227
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,840
and only by stepping on the enemy

228
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,440
can she survive.

229
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,480
You know what?

230
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,480
I gave her everything.

231
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,080
You can't protect her.

232
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,960
You couldn't protect her in the past

233
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,600
nor in the future.

234
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,560
And you have no right to do so.

235
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,240
Get out.

236
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:32,050
Don't you dare take a step outside!

237
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,670
Don't approach her.

238
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,440
Or, I'll fight you to the bitter end.

239
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,550
I mean what I say.
